{"tid":731763,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[社交平台] 點解香港咁少人用Twitter?","createTime":"2018-07-06T12:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T03:30:15.000Z","uid":16530,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c72b56911f288c69c65cf722e08bbb70db62870f","tid":731763,"uid":16530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"之前成日講嘅國際要事 美朝峰會 到而家中美貿易戰<br />\nDonald Trump都經常會係Twitter發表言論<br />\n好多新聞都會引用<br />\n<br />\n近期仲有泰國救少年足球隊嘅新聞<br />\n連Tesla&rsquo;s Elon Musk都用Twitter發表佢嘅意見<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/204345_83df8bc52743a5783810ce783df9910d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F204345_83df8bc52743a5783810ce783df9910d.png&h=605e50ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><br />\nMusk在Twitter中提及，可把一米寬的尼龍管道，伸進彎曲蜿蜒的洞穴隧道，然後打入空氣令其膨脹，或能造出一條水底隧道，用作泵水或其他救援用途。<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n講返日常少少, 日本人或者歐美地區都好多人會用<br />\n<br />\n我自己呢個年齡層(三四十歲) 身邊啲人都係用facebook, 其實d Content farm係facebook入面好多所謂趣聞 都係引用Twitter d料<br />\n<br />\n點解香港人咁少用Twitter呢個平台?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下連登仔 (我諗好多十幾廿歲巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n係咪你地嘅圈子都冇乜人用?"},{"pid":"d48063fd294bed6c43574226dd9a7d558ee3fbe8","tid":731763,"uid":18479,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"好似個個地方都唔同 台灣又興line 咁樣"},{"pid":"ea9b473c5c868bd5d489cec01273afff85b69382","tid":731763,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c72b56911f288c69c65cf722e08bbb70db62870f","tid":731763,"uid":16530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"之前成日講嘅國際要事 美朝峰會 到而家中美貿易戰<br />\nDonald Trump都經常會係Twitter發表言論<br />\n好多新聞都會引用<br />\n<br />\n近期仲有泰國救少年足球隊嘅新聞<br />\n連Tesla&rsquo;s Elon Musk都用Twitter發表佢嘅意見<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/204345_83df8bc52743a57